@module fmtcov/demo
@lang go
@version 0.1.0
@purpose Hermetic AID format coverage for loader and query integration tests
@depends [fmtcov/peer]

---

@type ErrKnown
@kind struct
@purpose Known error type referenced from @sig

---

@type Widget
@kind struct
@purpose Widget with fields and a method for HasMethod and FieldTouchers
@fields
  id: str — identifier
  count: int — counter
@methods TouchCount

---

@fn Widget.TouchCount
@purpose Reads count field via method
@sig (self) -> int

---

@trait Drawable
@purpose Trait for implements edge
@fields
  z: int — layer

---

@type ConcreteWidget
@kind struct
@purpose Type with extends, implements, and related
@extends [Widget]
@implements [Drawable]
@related [PeerDepTarget]

---

@const MaxWidgets
@purpose Upper bound constant
@type int

---

@fn MayFail
@purpose Produces known error from sig and orphan error from @errors
@sig () -> None ! ErrKnown
@errors
  OrphanError — not modeled as a type node

---

@fn ReadWidgetField
@purpose Accepts Widget so FieldTouchers finds it for Widget.count
@sig (w: Widget) -> None

---

@fn CalleeWithFx
@purpose Callee tagged with Db effects for SideEffects
@effects Db

---

@fn CallerChain
@purpose Calls CalleeWithFx for call graph and SideEffects traversal
@calls [CalleeWithFx]

---

@fn DependsEntry
@purpose Entry-level depends on cross-module type
@depends [PeerDepTarget]

---

@fn HelperFn
@purpose Resolved via dotted @calls suffix
@sig () -> None

---

@fn DottedCall
@purpose Calls using qualified-style name; loader resolves HelperFn by suffix
@calls [other.HelperFn]

---

@workflow demo_flow
@purpose Workflow with steps referencing real functions
@steps
  1. RunPipeline — first step
  2. FinalizePipeline — second step

---

@fn RunPipeline
@purpose Step target for demo_flow
@sig () -> None

---

@fn FinalizePipeline
@purpose Step target for demo_flow
@sig () -> None
